            . I am an apprentice to Mr. Richard Lamb. On the 11th of August, Mitchell came and gave me information; I went down the lane opposite, and found the prisoner with a leg of mutton which had been in the shop before.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18250915-160-person871">
                  EDWARD 
                  HANSON
               <interp inst="t18250915-160-person871" type="surname" value="HANSON"></interp>
